SHANE SMITH: We'd finally found
our North Koreans deep

00:00:11.300 --> 00:00:13.810
in the bush and were busy
talking to them when things

00:00:13.810 --> 00:00:15.370
started to get a bit hairy.

00:00:19.995 --> 00:00:21.940
Now these guys are
coming back here.

00:00:21.940 --> 00:00:23.912
The dude with the crowbar
is coming back.

